1.演者の初期配置
2.演出開始
General Atu: Did you summon me, my king?

King Agnos: First, please have a seat. It's going to be a
long conversation.
General Atu: Then, if you'll excuse me.
King Agnos: Atu, the time has come.
King Agnos: I think so, but what do you think?
General Atu: There's no need to think, my king.

General Atu: Please give me the order to 'Capture Tarasa'
like this.

King Agnos: That's it, the sword of the royal family.
That's it, the undefeated general. That's it, my friend!
General Atu: It's too kind of you to say so.
King Agnos: Atu...
King Agnos: I will take everything from Tarasa.
General Atu: As you command, my king.

Considering the age of Atu and King Agnos, it was highly
likely that this large-scale war would be their last. That's
why Atu couldn't hide his excitement.

At the same time, for a moment, Atu felt fear in King
Agnos's [eyes]. Atu had seen many eyes, but he felt that the
king's eyes were special. They were like the eyes of a
monster, as if they had lost their humanity.

King Agnos possessed a cruel and brutal side, such as
burning down an entire village because there were a few
bandits. Therefore, those who knew the king to be harboring
an ogre were aware of it.

I have to take it seriously and give it my all. The Second
Tarasa War is the biggest stage for Atu, but at the same
time, it is also an execution platform where failure is not
allowed.

If the invasion of Tarasa fails, Atu's head will roll. Atu
didn't value his own life, but he had resolved to die on the
battlefield. In such a situation, Atu found himself
laughing.
Because he was also one of the humans harboring a monster.
